(134, 45, 0, 1504468800, 'language', 'Samachablo', '<p>Samachablo is a Georgian historical district in Shida Kartli, Georgia, which lies entirely within the disputed South Ossetia Region. The name Samachablo derives from the Georgian aristocratic family of Machabeli who once held possession of the area.</p>', '', 'empty', 'en', 0, 1),
